#define GREETINGS ["How delicious, a morsel wanders into the pit. Begone, %s, before I decide you’d look better as ash.","Your soul smells like rot and wasted potential, %s. Flee my sight, or I shall feast.","A fragile thing, truly. Does the stench of sulfur frighten you yet, %s? It should.","I have no taste for such pathetic offerings. Crawl away, %s, while you still have legs to carry you.","You are not worthy of my shadow, let alone my time. Fade, %s.","Tremble, little creature. The abyss is watching, and it finds you... amusingly insignificant, %s.","Do you hear the whispers, %s? They are hungry for a life as fleeting as yours.","You dance on the precipice of oblivion. Tell me, %s, does the fall terrify you?","I shall let you live a while longer, %s. Despair makes the eventual end so much sweeter.","Your life is but a candle in a hurricane. Let me blow it out, %s.","You have a desperate kind of courage, %s. It will make your eventual demise all the more exquisite.","Step lightly, %s. These lands are stained with blood you could never hope to spill.","I have seen empires crumble; do you honestly believe you are a threat, %s?","Your essence is flickering, %s. I could snap your thread with a single thought.","I find your persistence... irritating. Cease your meddling, %s.","Welcome to the inferno, %s. I wonder how long your spirit will remain untainted here.","You possess a jagged soul. I might enjoy watching it shatter, %s.","I have tracked your path through the void, %s. It leads only to my doorstep.","You have a darkness in you, %s. It is the only thing that makes you tolerable.","Do not be deceived by my hospitality. The abyss has no mercy, %s.","A soul of substance. Tell me, %s, would you like to see what lies beyond the veil?","Your power is... pungent. It radiates like a fresh wound. I find it tempting, %s.","Many have sought to challenge me, %s. All of them now reside beneath my boots.","You are an interesting mutation of reality. Let us see how much of you is truth, %s.","Welcome, traveler. Your strength is a rare vintage. Let us see if it tastes as good as it looks, %s.","Your defiance warms the cold chambers of my heart, %s. It is... intoxicating.","You are a storm in the dark. I have missed such chaotic beauty, %s.","If you intend to bleed, %s, do it somewhere else. I only want your power.","We are cut from the same wretched cloth, %s. Join me, and we shall rewrite this reality.","Your strength is a beacon for the damned. Tell me, %s, are you ready to become a monster?","At last, an equal. My dark throne has been dreadfully empty, %s.","You radiate a power that tears at the seams of this world. I am... aroused by your potential, %s.","I have waited eons for a force like you to challenge the natural order. Let us begin our dance, %s.","Your presence consumes the very light around you. It is glorious, %s. Let us drown the world in it.","A god among worms. You and I, %s... we shall bring the apocalypse to their doorsteps."]
